metadata.name: J-Ball#1
metadata.description:
JPEX teamed up with Western Sydney Wanderers to launch 250 “J-Ball” NFTs.

The exclusively designed football NFT by JPEX range in a variety of colours with the Gold and Silver footballs unlocking the major prizes.

Follow us for more NFT update!
